        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Bob Hope Arlington Honors Act of 2003 - Directs the Secretary of the Army to permit the burial of Leslie Townes (Bob) Hope of California, an honorary veteran of the armed forces, in Arlington National Cemetery, Virginia, upon the request of his family.</p>]]></text>
